<br>
Fixes<br>
<br>
* Shaved 10 seconds of zoning for every subscriber.<br>
* Made it so familiars don't get agroed on.<br>
* Fixed several zone crash bugs<br>
* Changed a paladin spell - a design error in the spell trivialized several aspects of the high-end game.<br>
* Fixed several item and content problems.<br>
* Fixed several faction issues - some faction information released with Luclin deviated from norm.<br>
<br>
- The EverQuest Team<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
* Changed a paladin spell - a design error in the spell trivialized several aspects of the high-end game.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
What was the best spell we ever recieved, is now a 100 point mana sieve. <br>
<br>
Apparently being able to stop a dragon from ae'ing for 6 seconds is more broken then healing 6k hp with 1 spell. <br>
<br>
They nerf a spell with resist checks of mr+15, but not a spell that couldnt be resisted even if the recipient wanted it to.<br>
<br>
Dont worry, paladin still get group divine strength.<br>
<br>
And clerics still have that complete healing thing ive heard<br>
