<br>
The entire game was changed with Complete Heal.  Every high-level encounter was made more difficult because of that spell.  Creatures with 32 million hit points, AE silence, rampage and flurry were all created to conteract the power of Complete Heal.<br>
<br>
And because of the spell, the fights have become so one-dimensional.  The goal of all high-level strategies is to allow the clerics to heal the main tank efficiently and reliably.  The entire game centers around this one spell. <p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
